---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Preventative HVAC Maintenance | Comffordable Air Solutions" description="Proactive preventative maintenance plans for your HVAC system in St. Petersburg, Tampa, and Clearwater. Extend the life of your system and avoid costly breakdowns.">
    <main>
        <section class="hero" style="min-height: 60vh; align-items: center;">
            <img src="/images/pic_3.jpg" alt="HVAC technician performing comprehensive system maintenance" class="hero-bg-img" loading="eager" width="1920" height="1080" />
            <div class="hero-overlay" style="background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0,0,0,0.55), rgba(0,0,0,0.75));"></div>
            <div class="container hero-content text-center" style="margin: 0 auto;">
                <h1 style="font-size: 4.5rem; text-shadow: 2px 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.8); margin-bottom: 1rem;">HVAC Maintenance Plans <span class="text-purple">Tampa Bay, FL</span></h1>
                <p style="margin: 0 auto; font-size: 1.5rem; text-shadow: 1px 1px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.8); max-width: 800px;">
                    Reliable comfort. No surprises. Just peace of mind year-round.
                </p>
                <div style="margin-top: 2rem;">
                    <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary" style="font-size: 1.1rem; padding: 1rem 2rem;">Join Today & Save $31</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="process-section" style="padding-top: 4rem;">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="glass-panel" style="margin-bottom: 4rem; padding: 3rem; position: relative; overflow: hidden;">
                    <div style="position: absolute; top: 0; right: 0; background: var(--accent-color); color: #000; padding: 0.5rem 2rem; transform: rotate(45deg) translate(30%, -50%); font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.9rem;">
                        SPECIAL OFFER
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="text-center" style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
                        <h2 style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Simple. Affordable. Protected.</h2>
                        <p style="font-size: 1.25rem; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto 2rem;">
                            For just <strong class="text-purple">$23/month</strong> or <strong class="text-purple">$269/year</strong>, keep your system running at its best while avoiding costly breakdowns and unexpected repairs.
                        </p>
                        <div style="display: inline-block; background: rgba(30,136,229,0.1); padding: 1rem 2rem; border-radius: 50px; border: 1px solid var(--primary-purple);">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-tag text-purple" style="margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i>
                            <strong>Limited-Time Offer:</strong> Sign up today and save <strong>$31</strong> on your membership
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr)); gap: 3rem;">
                        <div class="animate-on-scroll">
                            <h3 style="border-bottom: 2px solid var(--primary-purple); padding-bottom: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                                <i class="fa-solid fa-list-check text-purple" style="margin-right: 0.75rem;"></i>What’s Included
                            </h3>
                            <ul style="list-style: none; color: var(--text-secondary);">
                                <li style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-purple" style="margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i> Two full system tune-ups per year (Cooling & Heating)</li>
                                <li style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-purple" style="margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i> Complete system inspection & performance check</li>
                                <li style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-purple" style="margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i> Outdoor condenser coil cleaning</li>
                                <li style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-purple" style="margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i> Indoor coil inspection with cleaning recommendations</li>
                                <li style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-purple" style="margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i> Electrical inspection & tightening of all connections</li>
                                <li style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-purple" style="margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i> Full drain line flush + 1-year no-clog guarantee</li>
                                <li style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-purple" style="margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i> Up to 1 lb of refrigerant included if needed</li>
                                <li style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-purple" style="margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i> Thermostat testing & calibration</li>
                                <li style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-purple" style="margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i> Blower motor inspection & performance check</li>
                                <li style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-purple" style="margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i> Filter check/replacement (customer-provided)</li>
                                <li style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-purple" style="margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i> Safety control testing</li>
                                <li style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-purple" style="margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i> Detailed system performance report after each visit</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="animate-on-scroll" style="transition-delay: 0.2s;">
                            <h3 style="border-bottom: 2px solid var(--primary-purple); padding-bottom: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                                <i class="fa-solid fa-star text-purple" style="margin-right: 0.75rem;"></i>Member-Only Benefits
                            </h3>
                            <ul style="list-style: none; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 3rem;">
                                <li style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-plus text-purple" style="margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i> <strong>FREE</strong> service calls (no diagnostic fees)</li>
                                <li style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-plus text-purple" style="margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i> <strong>15% OFF</strong> all repairs and parts</li>
                                <li style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-plus text-purple" style="margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i> Priority scheduling—especially during peak season</li>
                                <li style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-plus text-purple" style="margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i> No after-hours or emergency service fees</li>
                                <li style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-plus text-purple" style="margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i> Loyalty pricing on system replacements</li>
                                <li style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-plus text-purple" style="margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i> Transferable plan (great for homeowners selling)</li>
                            </ul>

                            <h3 style="border-bottom: 2px solid var(--primary-purple); padding-bottom: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                                <i class="fa-solid fa-house-chimney text-purple" style="margin-right: 0.75rem;"></i>Why Choose This Plan
                            </h3>
                            <ul style="list-style: none; color: var(--text-secondary);">
                                <li style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-shield-heart text-purple" style="margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i> Prevent costly breakdowns before they happen</li>
                                <li style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-shield-heart text-purple" style="margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i> Lower monthly energy bills with efficiency</li>
                                <li style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-shield-heart text-purple" style="margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i> Extend the life of your HVAC equipment</li>
                                <li style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-shield-heart text-purple" style="margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i> Stay protected with our drain line guarantee</li>
                                <li style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-shield-heart text-purple" style="margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i> Get service fast—even during hottest days</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="text-center" style="margin-top: 4rem; padding-top: 2rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--glass-border);">
                        <p style="font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 2rem;">No stress. No surprises. Just reliable comfort all year long.</p>
                        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary" style="font-size: 1.25rem; padding: 1.25rem 3rem;">Join for $23/month or $269/year</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg-dark), var(--bg-darker)); border-top: 1px solid var(--glass-border); padding: 5rem 0;">
            <div class="container animate-on-scroll">
                <div class="section-title">
                    <span>The Florida Difference</span>
                    <h2>Why Florida Homes Need Year-Round Maintenance</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="glass-panel" style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.9; color: var(--text-secondary);">
                    <p>Most HVAC manufacturers recommend a maintenance tune-up once per year. In Florida, that recommendation does not go far enough. Tampa Bay area homes run their air conditioning systems an average of 10 to 11 months per year, compared to 4 to 6 months in northern states. That is nearly twice the mechanical wear. Components that last three seasons elsewhere can degrade within one to two years here without proactive care, leading to repairs or full system replacements that could have been prevented entirely.</p>
                    <p>Florida's humidity creates specific maintenance challenges that simply do not exist in drier climates. Condensate drain lines carry moisture from the air handler to the exterior and can clog with algae and biological growth rapidly in our warm, humid environment. A single blocked drain line can overflow inside your air handler, causing water damage to ceilings, walls, and flooring that costs far more to fix than any maintenance plan. Our twice-annual tune-up program includes a full drain line flush and our exclusive one-year no-clog guarantee, giving you real protection against one of Florida's most common HVAC failures.</p>
                    <p>Salt air from Tampa Bay and the Gulf Coast accelerates oxidation on outdoor condenser coils and electrical terminals, quietly reducing system efficiency by 10 to 15 percent before any symptom appears on your thermostat or energy bill. Regular coil cleaning, electrical connection tightening, and refrigerant level verification, all included in our Comfort Membership Plan, keep your system running at factory efficiency. This is the kind of <a href="/maintenance" class="text-purple" style="font-weight:600;">proactive care</a> that protects your investment and keeps your family comfortable through even the most brutal Florida summers.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="faq-section">

            <div class="container">
                <div style="height: 1100px"><iframe src="https://www.localmarketingmanager.com/api/questions/comffordable-air-solutions-frequently-asked-questions?textColor=%23000000&backgroundColor=%23ffffff&showTitle=true&borderRadius=10px&visibility=showAllExpanded&isTransparentBackgroundApplied=false" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; border: none;" loading="lazy" id="ai-seo-iframe"></iframe></div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>
